Dear RICHARD:

Make a New Year's Resolution; help an ASME Student Member! 
Recruit a new member and 50% of the First Year Dues will be spent on Scholarships.
 
ASME membership offers professional & personal development through:

* NETWORKING OPPORTUNITIES
* LATEST TECHNICAL INFORMATION
* CAREER SERVICES 
* CONTINUING EDUCATION INSTITUTE
* Up to 20 % DISCOUNTS ON PUBLICATIONS
* VALUE-ADDED PROGRAMS (Home & Auto Insurances, Career Fairs, Professional Liability Insurances, etc.)
* AND MORE!

Here's how to participate:
1. Print your name and membership number on the Sponsor's Name line of the attached application. Make copies.
2. Discuss the benefits of joining ASME and distribute membership applications to your colleagues.
3. For additional applications call 800-THE-ASME (800-843-2763); outside North America call 973-882-1167 or access the downloadable application at: http://www.asme.org/pdf/member/expresapnmme01.pdf
4. Follow up with new members that you recruited to welcome them to ASME.
Visit http://www.asme.org/membershipdrive/
for complete campaign details. 


HAPPY NEW YEAR,
Cheryl Hasan
